    Shipping Times
    *NOTE* Orders Ship Out within 2 Business Days, unless Otherwise Noted. Once a package ships out, it usually takes from 2 to 7 business days to arrive for delivery within the US depending upon the Shipping Method selected. International orders will take from a minimum of 5-7 business days (Priority Mail) and at extreme times up to 2-3 Months to arrive if shipped via Regular/1st Class International Mail.
